snippet.title: Evidence proving Amber Heard was abusive to Johnny Depp (in under 5 minutes)
snippet.description:
This is a quick roundup of evidence proving Amber Heard was abusing Johnny Depp. This is for those who don't have time to review all the evidence; from people who are not fans, people who work for the media, for people who seem to think men cannot be abused. Anyone really. 

Yes, I know the editing is horribly cluttered and I'm sorry for that. There was just too much to include. Pause the statements to have enough time to read them. I thought they were too crucial to be left out. 

So, Amber supporters, I'm interested to know if you could wrap up something like this that proves she was the victim. Hmm... very likely not.
